Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.59,0:00:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Light so glaring that it can't be hidden shatters the silence and revives in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.50,0:00:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The violently quaking and thirsty Earth stakes its life and clashes together with sparks
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.30,0:00:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just one more time is enough to create a miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.43,0:00:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the power to regain the pages of memory lost in the past
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.44,0:00:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fs30}The believing heart that penetrates the darkness searches for the place where its soul sleeps
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.69,0:00:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And burns a sharp glance of eyes that can't sparkle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.12,0:01:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Two hearts of light and shadow head toward the future that the crystal reflects
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.46,0:01:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now they start to move, these eyes brimming red
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.80,0:01:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Diabound was defeated by Mahado.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And Bakura turned into sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.74,0:01:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But time stopped for no reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.74,0:01:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Millennium Items were taken by Akhenaden
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.77,0:01:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and placed upon the Stone Tablet of the Underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.74,0:01:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why? Wasn't it my victory?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.71,0:01:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I regained consciousness, a huge table was in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.22,0:01:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So this world is itself a Dark R.P.G?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.09,0:01:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The High Priest of Darkness"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.62,0:02:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.32,0:02:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Akhenaden...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.59,0:02:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you said earlier...\N Was it the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.49,0:02:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I am your son?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.63,0:02:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is the truth, my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.47,0:02:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very soon the Great Wicked God Zorc will be revived.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.50,0:02:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come join forces with us\N to defeat that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.71,0:02:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that, you will be able to become the Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.58,0:02:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Akhenaden... is my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.45,0:02:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.21,0:02:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not listen to this foolish man who has sold his soul to the Wicked God.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.69,0:02:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto, you are a priest who serves the Gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.12,0:03:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should fight hand in hand with the Pharaoh to protect this country and the people!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.93,0:03:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.96,0:03:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to the royal blood that is flowing within you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.93,0:03:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must heed to what\N this voice is telling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.43,0:03:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't go against your fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.74,0:03:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy is... Bakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.68,0:03:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.62,0:03:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi! Deadbeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're unconscious...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.78,0:03:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.81,0:03:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto, don't be misled!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.08,0:04:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's our duty to protect this land and our country!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.19,0:04:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why we must defeat Zorc!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.66,0:04:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can we allow such evil to destroy our precious motherland?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.76,0:04:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. Precious motherland?
Comment: 0,0:04:11.26,0:04:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let me ask you something...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.13,0:04:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who has been protecting this land...this country?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.93,0:04:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.54,0:04:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.20,0:04:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then perhaps it is your father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to say, Akhenaden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.31,0:04:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My useless brother, Akhenamkhanen, was unable to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.32,0:04:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all {\i1}myself,{\i0} his younger brother! It was all {\i1}me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dear brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.00,0:04:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, Pharaoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.83,0:04:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Denied! There has to be another option other than waging war in this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But Pharaoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.61,0:05:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That country is eying our country and has started building up their military forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If we do not strike them first...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.58,0:05:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Silence! Say no more, Akhenaden!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.32,0:05:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry, younger brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.19,0:05:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know very well that you are concerned about me and this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.46,0:05:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I do not wish to resort to wars to resolve our problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pharaoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.40,0:05:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hatred breeds new hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Such battles will continue\N forever without end.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.91,0:05:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please understand, Akhenaden.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.38,0:05:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was right in my views.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.18,0:05:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that foolish Pharaoh, thousands of soldiers died on the battlefields.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.13,0:05:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite that, he was revered as God.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.94,0:06:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was no doubt the Pharaoh and nothing but that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.24,0:06:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made up my mind then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That if my elder brother is the "light", then I shall become the "shadows".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.58,0:06:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it means getting staining my hands with blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.62,0:06:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Subsequently, I used the power of the Millennium Items and the country was saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.52,0:06:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... my brother was saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.96,0:07:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why, Sir Akhenaden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.03,0:07:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you cared for the former king, Akhenamkhanen, so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.14,0:07:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why betray him now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.01,0:07:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shimon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not use lowly terms like "betray" to describe the relationship I had with my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.35,0:07:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You only used King Akhenamkhanen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.42,0:07:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are only deceiving yourself... You have darkness within yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.52,0:07:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Hasan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.12,0:07:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you are really the guardian of the former Pharaoh, you should be very well aware!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About the details of the birth of Akhenamkhanen and me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.60,0:07:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should know fully well that we were {\i1}twins! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.96,0:07:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twins?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.40,0:07:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were born at the same time...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.73,0:07:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the one chosen as the elder brother was Akhenamkhanen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.54,0:07:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that was {\i1}only{\i0} because his cries were {\i1}louder{\i0} than mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.84,0:07:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew {\i1}that much{\i0} about it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.95,0:07:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akhenaden...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.62,0:07:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I still served my elder brother with all my might.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.59,0:07:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I deserted my wife and Seto...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.46,0:08:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went so far as to cover my hands in the blood of sin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My loyalty never wavered!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Seto...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came back. You returned to my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.61,0:08:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto... Don't you feel that this is the work of fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.12,0:08:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was brought up by my mother believing that my father died on the battlefields.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.59,0:08:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wanted to be a priest, in order to serve the country and the Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.00,0:08:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was always you, Lord Akhenaden, who supported me during these times.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.70,0:08:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In my eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.37,0:08:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You were like a father to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.87,0:08:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.02,0:09:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You took extra care of me because you knew that I was your son!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.39,0:09:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But so did you reveal that you were my father {\i0}now{\i1}...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.77,0:09:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.93,0:09:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about the White Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.67,0:09:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That white dragon now drives your fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.64,0:09:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto, you are the chosen one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.47,0:09:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The White Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.19,0:09:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does the White Dragon symbolize my fate in becoming the Pharaoh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.76,0:09:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,White Dragon...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.63,0:09:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue-Eyes White Dragon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.90,0:09:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.40,0:09:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the Great Wicked God Zorc revives, everything in this world will be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.77,0:10:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What meaning is there in becoming the Pharaoh after that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.35,0:10:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto, do not get confused!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.48,0:10:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.35,0:10:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Akhenaden!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.49,0:10:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still not understand, Seto?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.12,0:10:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the almighty Great Wicked God Zorc revives,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.36,0:10:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this country will become the World of Darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.73,0:10:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will worship the Great Wicked God Zorc as our God and create a new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.13,0:10:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Pharaoh who governs this new world is you, Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.94,0:10:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must become the King of Darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.37,0:10:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King of Darkness...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.31,0:10:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, your destiny is fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.38,0:10:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to me, your father!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.75,0:10:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.68,0:10:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.02,0:10:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Lord Seto...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.36,0:10:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't go...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.87,0:11:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on now, Seto.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.78,0:11:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.54,0:11:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.88,0:11:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... The White Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.29,0:11:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto, you are the true king!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.79,0:11:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop messing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.46,0:11:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no telling for sure if this land will be shrouded in darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.43,0:11:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto, we must stand united and defeat the Great Wicked God Zorc!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.46,0:11:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.76,0:11:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Seto!\N - Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.40,0:11:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.27,0:11:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not be swayed! Come, Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.38,0:11:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akhenaden!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.24,0:11:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, who has been taken over by darkness, has no right to talk about the king!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.35,0:11:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not wish to hear that from {\i1}you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.72,0:11:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If so, I shall wait for Lord Zorc's revival...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.49,0:11:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I shall kill the Pharaoh and snuff out all the light!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.23,0:11:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let your soul rot, Pharaoh! Join that cursed Akhenamkhanen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.23,0:12:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hasan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.80,0:12:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pharaoh, I will hold him off here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.90,0:12:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not let you get injured!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.80,0:12:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hasan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.11,0:12:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Seto...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.02,0:12:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, run along!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.26,0:12:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be in a fix if you\N don't get to Seto's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.16,0:12:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starving...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.57,0:12:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no food left...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.14,0:12:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This guy was the only one who could move when I stopped time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.64,0:12:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Does it mean that this Non Player Character is out of both Yugi's and my control?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.25,0:12:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Fatty, what is your role in this game?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:12:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop messing around, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.69,0:13:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Honda?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.70,0:13:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing much...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.23,0:13:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Bobasa crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.63,0:13:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How would I know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.63,0:13:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Bobasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.04,0:13:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starving~!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.17,0:13:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suddenly feel very hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.98,0:13:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I can't move anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.08,0:13:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I smell food.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.68,0:13:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could this be the warehouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.92,0:13:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! But this place is all empty!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.05,0:13:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobasa, don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.06,0:13:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You finished everything..?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.73,0:13:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You jerk! You shoulda left a little for us, at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I am really hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.37,0:13:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we shouldn't be wasting time here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.77,0:13:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try to find Pharaoh's name quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.44,0:13:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you say so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.07,0:13:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've looked everywhere but found nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.71,0:13:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably not in the royal palace, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.98,0:13:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think the same too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.45,0:13:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's not here, then it should be somewhere else...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.75,0:13:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's head off then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.32,0:14:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.69,0:14:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No use wasting time here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobasa really starving! Can't walk anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're dealing with it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.59,0:14:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.46,0:14:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's just leave this guy here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.76,0:14:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's of no use anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.30,0:14:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... You're right, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.70,0:14:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon... I feel bad for him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.27,0:14:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can we do since he can't move anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.64,0:14:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least, we could find some food for Bobasa to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.44,0:14:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. It's the least we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.38,0:14:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.42,0:14:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys serious...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.29,0:14:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What the hell are these guys thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.46,0:14:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Have they gone mad from their hunger?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:14:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobasa is hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.94,0:14:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just.. a bit more, Bobasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.84,0:15:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our hands'll just pass right through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.38,0:15:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one who eat it, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.99,0:15:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobasa, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.69,0:15:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grapes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.23,0:15:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're so exhausted...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.96,0:15:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.97,0:15:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we've found it for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.13,0:15:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat it, Bobasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.27,0:15:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.47,0:15:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really okay? Is it really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.84,0:15:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Argh, just eat it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.18,0:15:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or I'm gonna eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.95,0:15:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at how satisfied he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.99,0:15:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.09,0:15:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy for you, Bobasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.39,0:15:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.63,0:15:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Bobasa is very full now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.80,0:15:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll grant you guys a wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.17,0:15:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on everyone, get on my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.50,0:15:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.90,0:16:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to Bobasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, let's do as Bobasa says!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.38,0:16:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.18,0:16:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will it be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.12,0:16:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of you want to know\N Pharaoh's name right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.49,0:16:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobasa, do you know Pharaoh's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.76,0:16:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.23,0:16:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.73,0:16:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may not know his name, but I know where his name is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.86,0:16:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get you at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.43,0:16:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This guy must be a crucial part of the game's scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's an important "switch" for the whereabouts of the Eighth Key.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If not for Yugi and the rest, I would have missed this "switch".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.39,0:16:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The "Bo" in Bobasa\N is the "Bo" "Bobbing Glutton"~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.03,0:16:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The "Ba" in Bobasa is\N the "Ba" in "Dinner Bash"~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.76,0:17:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The "Bo" in Bobasa\N is the "Bo" "Bobbing Glutton"~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Bobasa seems so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.37,0:17:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The "Ba" in Bobasa is\N the "Ba" in "Dinner Bash"~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Enough with the "Bo"...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.60,0:17:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}But what about the "Sa" in his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.88,0:17:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.44,0:17:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can that be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.91,0:17:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Valley of the Kings!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.68,0:17:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Valley of the Kings is where all the Pharaoh's tombs are, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.85,0:17:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.98,0:17:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that the Pharaoh's tomb is built even before he is born.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.42,0:17:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A place as holy as a Pharaoh's tomb...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.59,0:17:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My other self's name must be here. Nobody erased it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.97,0:17:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've finally reached\N where the Eighth Key is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Many thanks, Bobasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.14,0:17:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobasa should thank you all instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.24,0:17:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of you have been so nice to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can be so full because all of you let me have the bunch of grapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.65,0:17:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason, I suddenly feel full too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.69,0:17:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.35,0:17:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strange... Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.29,0:17:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the reason we've\N been feeling so hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.46,0:18:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.79,0:18:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I'm not hungry anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.13,0:18:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.06,0:18:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,..But?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.07,0:18:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The "Bo" in Bobasa\N is the "Bo" "Bobbing Glutton"~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.87,0:18:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The "Ba" in Bobasa is\N the "Ba" in "Dinner Bash"~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.51,0:18:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The "Sa" in Bobasa is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.21,0:18:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}He's singing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.54,0:18:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Sayonara"~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.18,0:18:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.92,0:18:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.12,0:18:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.72,0:18:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.25,0:18:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Bobasa!\N - Bobasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.16,0:18:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now{\i0} it makes sense...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.23,0:18:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.66,0:18:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your partners are quite efficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.77,0:18:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're quite close to finding your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.67,0:18:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My partner...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.97,0:18:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you know about that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.87,0:18:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masters should have no way of knowing what the None Player Characters are doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.31,0:18:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}do{\i0} wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.05,0:19:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's countdown to my... No...\N to Great Wicked God Zorc's revival!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.59,0:19:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The climax is approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.89,0:19:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if the main cast \Ndoesn't make a move...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.83,0:19:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this will become {\i1}boring.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.33,0:19:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hasan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.04,0:19:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your pawn is quite a tough nut to crack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.57,0:19:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you run around \Ndoing as you please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.24,0:19:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me add some twists to the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.61,0:19:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If our lead actor isn't here to witness the revival of the Great Wicked God Zorc...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.08,0:19:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it would be too much of a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.09,0:19:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lead actor?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.39,0:19:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You used it once before yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.42,0:19:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you'd call "Transferring {\i1}Ba{\i0}"!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.89,0:19:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got it from your partner before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.93,0:19:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pull yourself together, Other Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're here with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.33,0:19:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.80,0:19:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still have power remaining...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.77,0:19:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Power within my irreplaceable friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.87,0:20:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I shall use that on {\i1}my{\i0} pawn as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.71,0:20:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your pawn?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.15,0:20:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I've invited someone interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.68,0:20:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring him into this world and use some of his {\i1}Ba{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.72,0:20:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time for your debut, President!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.89,0:20:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't mean that Kaiba's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.13,0:20:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What... is this light?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.58,0:20:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.05,0:20:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.29,0:20:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna borrow your soul, Kaiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a {\i1}little,{\i0} though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.37,0:20:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.70,0:21:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will still choose to stand by the Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.91,0:21:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.03,0:21:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back, my dear Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.83,0:21:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pawn will always remain a pawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.50,0:21:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These guys aren't enough for a finale.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.07,0:21:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without me around, this game cannot come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.77,0:21:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.76,0:21:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To show us now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.03,0:22:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...a map isn't needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.50,0:22:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only what tore apart the darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.68,0:22:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the hope that lies in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.82,0:22:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without deciding on a goal...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.19,0:22:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll just take a step toward my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.87,0:22:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}EYE'S, while I feel them...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.34,0:22:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll find your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.95,0:22:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh! EYE'S, if what I wished for...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.22,0:23:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...shudders my very soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.73,0:23:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...a Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.84,0:23:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobasa disappeared after bringing us to where the Pharaoh's name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.68,0:23:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Bobasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.32,0:23:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will surely find how the Pharaoh's real name!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.39,0:23:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't this the tomb where Yugi's Grandfather found the Millennium Puzzle long ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.13,0:23:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, the revived Bakura separated the Pharaoh from rest...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.20,0:23:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to prevent them from helping the Pharaoh when Zorc is revived.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.43,0:23:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.13,0:23:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Countdown to the Revival of the Great Wicked God"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.27,0:23:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please look forward to it!
